subject: Tennis
Wimbledon Tennis Tournament
lead_paragraph: The United States is shut out of the late rounds at Wimbledon, but Canada will send Milos Raonic into the men’s semifinals Friday and Eugenie Bouchard into the women’s final Saturday.
